@node About "What is Sam?"

	@{u}About Sam.@{uu}

Sam is a very simple and quite small sound datatype player. If your Workbench has  datatype support you may use this program to play samples. The main advantage of this program is that is small yet contains some useful commands.

Sam requires datatypes library v40+ to function as it takes advantage of the SDTA_SignalTask tag.

